          exc: "С <em>I am</em> → <em>aren't I?</em>; с <em>Let's</em> → <em>shall we?</em>; с императивом → <em>will you? / won't you?</em>. После <em>nobody/no one/nothing</em> в хвостике — положительный: <em>Nobody came, did they?</em>",
