            '<s>Neither answers is right</s> → <em>Neither answer is right</em> — после <em>neither</em> ед.ч.',
            "<s>I don't like neither</s> → <em>I don't like either</em> — не двойное отрицание.",
            '<s>Both my parents is</s> → <em>Both my parents are</em> — мн.ч.',
