          unitUrl: 'https://ok-english.ru/unit-107-red/',
          exp: "<strong>Unit 107</strong> — устойчивые выражения с предлогами места (Unit 2).<br><br><p>Запоминаются блоками — логика не всегда буквальна.</p><p>С <strong>at</strong>:</p><ul><li><em>at home, at work, at school, at university, at the airport, at the station, at a concert / party / meeting</em>.</li><li><em>at the top / bottom, at the end of (the street)</em>.</li></ul><p>С <strong>in</strong>:</p><ul><li><em>in hospital, in prison, in bed</em> (как состояние).</li><li><em>in the middle, in the front / back of (the car)</em>.</li><li><em>in a photo, in a picture, in a book, in a newspaper, in a queue / row / line</em>.</li></ul><p>С <strong>on</strong>:</p><ul><li><em>on holiday, on business, on a trip / tour / cruise / journey</em>.</li><li><em>on TV, on the radio, on the phone, on the internet, on the menu, on page 5, on a farm, on an island</em>.</li></ul><p>Примеры: <em>He's on holiday in Spain. I saw it on TV last night. There are three people in the picture.</em></p><p>Контрастные пары: <em>in hospital</em> (пациент, BrE) vs <em>in the hospital</em> (AmE / посетитель); <em>at the end</em> (в конце чего-то) vs <em>in the end</em> (в конце концов).</p>",
