            '<s>If she had came, we would have seen her.</s> → <em>If she had come, we would have seen her.</em> — V3 от <em>come</em> — <em>come</em>.',
            '<s>If you listened, you would pass.</s> (о прошлом) → <em>If you had listened, you would have passed.</em> — полный Тип 3.',
