          unitUrl: 'https://ok-english.ru/unit-30-green/',
          exp: "<strong>Unit 30</strong> (Advanced) — глагол + -ing или + to-infinitive: системный обзор.<br><br><strong>Только герундий (-ing):</strong> <em>enjoy, avoid, finish, mind, miss, practise, suggest, consider, deny, admit, delay, postpone, resist, risk, imagine, involve, keep, fancy, can't help, can't stand, give up, put off, feel like</em>. <em>I enjoy reading; She suggested going; We can't afford to waste time.</em><br><br><strong>Только инфинитив (to + V):</strong> <em>want, hope, decide, plan, expect, promise, refuse, offer, manage, afford, agree, fail, seem, appear, tend, pretend, intend, threaten, choose, learn, deserve</em>. <em>I hope to see you soon.</em><br><br><strong>Обе формы с разным смыслом:</strong><ul><li><em>remember/forget + -ing</em> = прошлое воспоминание; + <em>to V</em> = будущая обязанность: <em>I remember locking the door</em> vs <em>Remember to lock the door.</em></li><li><em>stop + -ing</em> = прекратить процесс; + <em>to V</em> = остановиться, чтобы: <em>He stopped smoking</em> vs <em>He stopped to smoke.</em></li><li><em>regret + -ing</em> = сожалеть о прошлом; + <em>to inform/say/tell</em> = формально сообщать с сожалением: <em>We regret to inform you…</em></li><li><em>go on + -ing</em> = продолжать то же; + <em>to V</em> = перейти к другому: <em>He went on talking</em> vs <em>He went on to become a minister.</em></li></ul><br><strong>Обе формы без разницы смысла:</strong> <em>begin, start, continue, bother, love, like, hate, prefer</em> (с лёгкими оттенками: -ing общее удовольствие, to V конкретное намерение).",
          exc: '<p><em>remember/forget/regret + -ing</em> — прошлое; + <em>to</em> — будущее/обязанность.</p><p><em>stop + -ing</em> — прекратить; + <em>to</em> — остановиться чтобы.</p>',
